data.description: BEAUTIFUL 4 BED, 3.5 BATHS, 2 STORY LENNAR HOME with gameroom, study, formal dining, fireplace & covered patio. 2nd Master suite with kitchenette and living. Granite, crown molding, full sod, full sprinkler, GE Stainless appliances with fridge & gas range included.  Ceramic tile in entry, kitchen, nook, baths & utility. ENERGY EFFICIENT features incl RADIANT BARRIER, high-efficiency HVAC, LOW E Glass. Wi-Fi Certified Smart Home powered by Amazon Alexa! 2 Community pools, Splash Park & playground. Tennis courts, jogging trail & hockey rink! Move in ready! List price includes builder discounts. Ready July 2018!
